* There was so much battle and her charges seemed to have almost no effect 
on MotorMaster, but she looked in worry as she saw what she really didn't 
feel like seeing.
He was...contracting and everything...to form a gustalt!
No!
Not one of those, anything but one of those!
In battle everything was fine until the enemy brought in those heavy 
hitters, turning the tables right away and making it so that victory for the 
Maximals was almost inpossable.
Just then it felt like a bolt of lightning sent though her spine, maining 
her retract the guns and waver a bit to keep her belence.
A pair of dark eyes glared from the back of her head.*

SBM: " Thought I was gone, huh?"

* Cool and calm that voice was, something she remembered all to well.
It was the reawakening of her second beast mode.
This could mean trouble!*
